creator: cohesionIB
descriptionHtml:
Experience improved productivity and greater satisfaction at work with COHESION.

Conveniently use the single COHESION portal, available in web and mobile interfaces, for turn-key submissions and visibility to progress for visitor management, service requests, amenity booking, dock and freight elevator booking, parking management, bike room reservations and flex office space reservations.

Easily access building and on-site amenities with mobile access key card at digital card readers.

Quickly access building information, including contact information and availability of on-site amenities, such as, conference and meeting spaces, parking, bike room and fitness center, as well as, direct information and links to on-site restaurants, ATM machines, sundry shop and package center.

Streamlined communications provide easier direct contact between you, your building and nearby amenities. Contact building operations more quickly with hyperlinked phone numbers and email addresses in the app. Engage with nearby restaurants and retail more easily with direct links to their websites. Receive information more quickly via building push notifications regarding emergency alerts, building events and general announcements.

Note: Some app features are only available to current occupants of the building with valid credentials.
descriptionShort: A one-stop-shop for self-service capabilities & access to info at your building
